data.description: Awesome Garden Home in Midtown Bryant. Explore this remarkable Craftsman style home located in one of Bryant's newest developments! This custom-designed residence boasts a variety of distinctive features, including crown molding throughout and custom window trim. The kitchen and bathroom vanities feature elegant quartz countertops, while the master bath includes a spacious walk-in shower and an illuminated defrosting mirror. For added convenience, both the master bedroom and living room windows are equipped with remote-controlled shades. Luxury vinyl plank flooring graces the majority of the living spaces, with ceramic tile flooring adorning the bathrooms. The utility room is exceptionally spacious, offering ample room for a freezer. The kitchen is well-appointed with under-cabinet lighting, a generous pantry, and a stylish bar area. You'll also appreciate the ease of a gas log fireplace that ignites at the flip of a switch. Furthermore, every room is wired with Cat-5 for seamless internet connectivity. As an added bonus, the subdivision provides access to a swimming pool and a picnic area exclusively for residents. This home won't last long!
